{"id": "1448630619671232563", "channel_id": "1448630619671232563", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "If you have a card with 3 Stacks of Fiamma and you discard it, the Kath Posse can draw it and give it 1, so it has 4 or more Fiamma.\nIt can also put 1 Fiamma stack on her Rouse card, that normally shouldn't be possible.", "timestamp": "2025-12-11T11:00:53.985000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-11T11:01:23.941000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1448630620732526592", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1134084, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1448630619671232563/1448630620732526592/image.png?ex=6a006566&is=69ff13e6&hm=6bbeebd607077c2953db577ccb8123c942576c56e2aacb6e7203b78de5baf3a3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1448630619671232563", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Kath Posse Extra Fiamma bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1448572725965750374", "channel_id": "1448572725965750374", "type": 0, "author_id": "1440716849225400351", "author_name": "liao_54332", "author_bot": false, "content": "密契养成（就刷一条合适副属性的基本养成）和唤醒体天赋消耗的蔷薇金卷消耗巨大，能不能加大一些蔷薇金卷的获取途径呀。这次柱子活动之后开始准备洗几套50%-60%的密契  结果发现笔和印章都还有盈余的情况，蔷薇金卷最先没了。是我玩的少还是培养的问题吗，我感觉这个蔷薇金卷的大头来源居然是不知道什么时候邮件（500W！！！）<:question2:1356053130336272414> <:question2:1356053130336272414>", "timestamp": "2025-12-11T07:10:51.050000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1448572725965750374", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」关于蔷薇金卷的获取", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
